---
import "../style/base.css";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 ページが見つかりません - Dragonsweeper</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="index, nofollow">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://www.dragonsweepers.net/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .error-message {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        .error-message h1 {
            font-size: 4em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-message p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="site-header">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="site-logo">
                <a href="/">Dragonsweeper</a>
            </div>
            <nav class="main-nav">
                <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="ナビゲーションを切り替える"><i class="fas fa-bars"></i></button>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">ホーム</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/#about">概要</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/#how-to-play">遊び方</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/#contact">お問い合わせ</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="mobile-menu">
        <span class="close-btn">×</span>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">ホーム</a></li>
            <li><a href="/#about">概要</a></li>
            <li><a href="/#how-to-play">遊び方</a></li>
            <li><a href="/#contact">お問い合わせ</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <main class="main-content">
        <section class="error-message">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>404</h1>
                <p>ページが見つかりません (Pēji ga mitsukarimasen)</p>
                <p>申し訳ありませんが、お探しのページは存在しないか、移動された可能性があります。(Mōshiwake arimasen ga, o sagashi no pēji wa sonzai shinai ka, idō sareta kanōsei ga arimasu.)</p>
                <p><a href="/">ホームページに戻る (Hōmupēji ni modoru)</a></p> <!-- Link to your homepage -->
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="container">
            <p>© 2025 Dragonsweeper. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

<script>
    const navToggle = document.querySelector('.nav-toggle');
    const mobileMenu = document.querySelector('.mobile-menu');
    const closeBtn = document.querySelector('.mobile-menu .close-btn');

    navToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
        mobileMenu.style.display = 'flex'; // Show the mobile menu
    });

    closeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        mobileMenu.style.display = 'none'; // Hide the mobile menu
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>